  <body>
    <section name="Usage">
      <subsection name="Install Sonar">
        <p>
          <a href="http://sonar.codehaus.org/downloads">Download</a>
          and
          <a href="http://sonar.codehaus.org/documentation/">install</a>
          Sonar. <b>Server must be up</b>
          before executing the Maven plugin.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Analyse project">
        <p>Run on your project root directory :
          <source><![CDATA[mvn sonar:sonar]]></source>
        </p>
        <p>For more details and advanced configuration, read the
          <a href="http://docs.codehaus.org/display/SONAR/The+2+minutes+tutorial">2 minutes tutorial</a>
          and the <a href="http://docs.codehaus.org/display/SONAR/Install+Sonar">installation guide</a>.
        </p>
      </subsection>

    </section>
  </body>
